channel.title: This is making me effing mad!
channel.description: I made my own server, it worked fine, then i tried to get the item fire cape, i got it but then it said connection lost, i was like no biggie right, then i logged back in and it worked but i couldnt move! then it said connection lost again, then i logged in again and this time it said. "error connecting to server. must be down. click cancel then start server to make your own." i started server again and it just repeats itself its like when i get some items i cant get back on that account, pleeeeease help me!!!!!! :mad: :mad: :mad:
